# F15 review IMPORTANT-1: cap protobuf to 7.x. Dockerfile pins
# protobuf<7 during proto-stub generation then re-installs >=7.34.1
# for the runtime venv; leaving protobuf unbounded risks a future
# resolution landing protobuf 8.x mid-build and breaking that
# carefully-staged install. <8 keeps us in the same major.
